						<p class="text-white text-5xl font-medium text-center mb-4">My Skills</p>
						<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
							<div class="border-2 border-[#101010] bg-[#090909] p-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                                <p class="text-white text-2xl font-medium text-center">Frontend</p>
                                <p class="text-gray-400 text-center">I have about 6 years of frontend development experience.</p>
